  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Blood donor recruitment is an important issue in every country, since the blood supply
      pressure become more and more intense. Donor retention is even more important, because it is
      easier to recruit an old customers than a new one. Therefore, figuring the most effective
      ways of recruiting lapsed blood donors and understanding the reasons of not donating blood
      again is critical and vital for the development of blood donation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
